$ HTML element input (type=text)

{ pattern #input-text-pattern

  The value of the `pattern` specifies a → development/regular-expressions[regular expression] that is checked against the entered value *when the form is submitted* (not when it is entered).

  gh|about-html|/tags/input/type/text/pattern.html||

}

The HTML → development/web/HTML/tags/input[`<input>`] element.
